# IElement interface

Representation of a single [element](https://docs.mendix.com/apidocs-mxsdk/mxsdk/understanding-the-metamodel#2-elements) in metamodel. This is an abstract element, so all instances of [`IElement`](./IElement.md) also implement more concrete interface like [`IMicroflow`](../Mendix.StudioPro.ExtensionsAPI.Model.Microflows/IMicroflow.md).

```csharp
public interface IElement : IStructure
```
